{"source": "https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/pinglun/weise/ws-06272023083341.html", "type": "NewsArticle", "published time": "2023-06-27T08:49:00-04:00", "modified time": "2023-06-27T08:57:47-04:00", "author": null, "publisher": {"type": "Organization", "name": "Radio Free Asia"}, "title": "\u8bc4\u8bba | \u552f\u8272\uff1a\u5f53\u6211\u4eec\u8c08\u8bba\u5929\u82b1\u65f6\u6211\u4eec\u5728\u8c08\u8bba\u4ec0\u4e48\uff08\u4e09\u5341\u516d\uff09", "videos": [], "audios": [], "text": "<img src=\"https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/pinglun/weise/ws-06272023083341.html/@@images/19ebe9c7-0ab3-4b2f-8abf-d90dd8558387.jpeg\"/>\n1943\u5e74\u65e5\u672c\u822a\u62cd\u53cc\u9ec4\u5bfa\n<a href=\"https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/pinglun/weise/ws-06272023083341.html/@@images/image\">\n <img src=\"https://www.rfa.org//++plone++rfa-resources/img/icon-zoom.png\"/>\n</a>\n\u7f51\u7edc\u622a\u56fe/\u552f\u8272\u63d0\u4f9b\n<!-- zoomattribute -->\n<img alt=\"6\u6708RFA\u8bc4\u8bba2-002.jpeg\" height=\"344\" src=\"https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/pinglun/weise/ws-06272023083341.html/tianhua/66708rfa8bc48bba2-002.jpeg/@@images/0aa34e4d-7606-4acc-88ba-4e1a98967cef.jpeg\" title=\"6\u6708RFA\u8bc4\u8bba2-002.jpeg\" width=\"620\"/>\n<p class=\"slideshow_caption\">\n \u4e1c\u9ec4\u5bfa\u5c71\u95e8\uff08\u62cd\u6444\u4e8e1909\u5e74\uff09\n</p>\n<img alt=\"6\u6708RFA\u8bc4\u8bba2-003.jpeg\" height=\"350\" src=\"https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/pinglun/weise/ws-06272023083341.html/tianhua/66708rfa8bc48bba2-003.jpeg/@@images/5fbc4579-ec70-4cc5-85ac-44f58f9c2fb8.jpeg\" title=\"6\u6708RFA\u8bc4\u8bba2-003.jpeg\" width=\"620\"/>\n<p class=\"slideshow_caption\">\n \u4e1c\u9ec4\u5bfa\u7891\u4ead\uff08\u5fb7\u56fd\u4eba\u62cd\u6444\u4e8e\u4e0a\u4e16\u7eaa\u56db\u5341\u5e74\u4ee3\uff09\n</p>\n<img alt=\"6\u6708RFA\u8bc4\u8bba2-004.jpeg\" height=\"416\" src=\"https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/pinglun/weise/ws-06272023083341.html/tianhua/66708rfa8bc48bba2-004.jpeg/@@images/4bb3a94f-9f78-46f4-b835-5c7f89741288.jpeg\" title=\"6\u6708RFA\u8bc4\u8bba2-004.jpeg\" width=\"620\"/>\n<p class=\"slideshow_caption\">\n \u4e1c\u9ec4\u5bfa\u5927\u4e58\u6bbf\uff08\u5fb7\u56fd\u4eba\u62cd\u6444\u4e8e\u4e0a\u4e16\u7eaa\u56db\u5341\u5e74\u4ee3\uff09\n</p>\n<img alt=\"6\u6708RFA\u8bc4\u8bba2-005.jpg\" height=\"453\" src=\"https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/pinglun/weise/ws-06272023083341.html/tianhua/66708rfa8bc48bba2-005.jpg/@@images/6127af2b-6263-423f-bfcf-61ef2845e04c.jpeg\" title=\"6\u6708RFA\u8bc4\u8bba2-005.jpg\" width=\"620\"/>\n<p class=\"slideshow_caption\">\n \u4e1c\u9ec4\u5bfa\u5929\u738b\u6bbf\u5929\u738b\u50cf\uff08\u5fb7\u56fd\u4eba\u62cd\u6444\u4e8e\u4e0a\u4e16\u7eaa\u56db\u5341\u5e74\u4ee3\uff09\n</p>\n<img alt=\"6\u6708RFA\u8bc4\u8bba2-006.jpg\" height=\"477\" src=\"https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/pinglun/weise/ws-06272023083341.html/tianhua/66708rfa8bc48bba2-006.jpg/@@images/a41637e8-10e4-4271-8fbb-a98b1bbf604f.jpeg\" title=\"6\u6708RFA\u8bc4\u8bba2-006.jpg\" width=\"620\"/>\n<p class=\"slideshow_caption\">\n \u4e1c\u9ec4\u5bfa\u5927\u4e58\u6bbf\u5185\u4f5b\u50cf\uff08\u65e5\u672c\u4eba\u62cd\u6444\u4e8e\u4e0a\u4e16\u7eaa\u56db\u5341\u5e74\u4ee3\uff09\n</p>\n<img alt=\"6\u6708RFA\u8bc4\u8bba2-007.jpg\" height=\"431\" src=\"https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/pinglun/weise/ws-06272023083341.html/tianhua/66708rfa8bc48bba2-007.jpg/@@images/2915347e-5bb9-45d7-8c75-7cd74f11fcd0.jpeg\" title=\"6\u6708RFA\u8bc4\u8bba2-007.jpg\" width=\"620\"/>\n<p class=\"slideshow_caption\">\n \u5fae\u535a\u622a\u56fe\n</p>\n<img alt=\"6\u6708RFA\u8bc4\u8bba2-008.jpeg\" height=\"465\" src=\"https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/pinglun/weise/ws-06272023083341.html/tianhua/66708rfa8bc48bba2-008.jpeg/@@images/1e661cc3-bebc-493c-8bf2-fc4b7e64268f.jpeg\" title=\"6\u6708RFA\u8bc4\u8bba2-008.jpeg\" width=\"620\"/>\n<p class=\"slideshow_caption\">\n \u4eca\u65e5\u4e1c\u9ec4\u5bfa\u5df2\u662f\u201c\u603b\u653f\u5927\u9662\u201d\uff08\u53cb\u4eba\u8fd1\u65e5\u62cd\u6444\uff09\n</p>\n<img alt=\"6\u6708RFA\u8bc4\u8bba2-009.jpeg\" height=\"465\" src=\"http